latestPosts.caption:
Con- graduation 🥂

Living the life of your dreams comes with obstacles and setbacks but with hards work, perseverance and self belief there is no limit to what you can achieve . 

To pursue my dreams and build a career in Fashion was one of the first and best significant decisions that would shape me into who I am today.  Studying at National Institute of Fashion Technology, Kolkata made it a reality. NIFT Kolkata where my passion for my chosen field blossomed and flourished. Most importantly, NIFT has given me a unique identity and a sense of purpose.

Reaching the milestone of post-graduation is a momentous occasion in one's life. And the third phase of my life came to an end on September 9, 2023, when I received my post-graduation degree in Masters of Fashion Management Studies from Dr. C V Anand Bose, the Governor of West Bengal, in the presence of our special guest, Sri Biren Kumar Basak, Padma Shri, and other respected dignitaries.

In these years of my college life have given me a wealth of experiences, numerous special bonds, blessings, and love from my respected faculties, all of which I will cherish forever❤ 

I would like to express sincere gratitude to all my professors, friends, seniors, and my lovely juniors who helped me achieve my long-sought goal. And lastly, I will only say love to Mamoni and Baba for letting me follow my passion and for your endless support in every choice of my life. 

Taking pride in my choice 😇

#classof2023 
#niftkolkataconvocationceremony2023 

( Phone photography was not allowed due to high security still I managed somehow )
